    "For the flow experiments, we used μ-Slide I Luer cell with a channel height of 0.8 mm, width of 0.5 mm, and length of 50 mm (Ibidi).",
    "Spirulina powder was purchased from Tree of Life (Japan).",
    "To convert MP concentration from mg L -1 to MPs L -1, the size distribution was considered (Suppl. Fig.",
    "17) following Eq. 1, according to ref.",
    "Where ρ is the density of polymer in g cm -1, D n is the diameter of the MP bead in µm, and P n is the percent content of this fraction."
